user_question: What events are happening in London this weekend?
expected_sql_query: SELECT e.name, o.start_at_utc, v.name FROM events e JOIN event_occurrences o ON e.id = o.event_id JOIN venues v ON o.venue_id = v.id WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(v.city, '$.en') LIKE '%London%' AND o.start_at_utc BETWEEN [weekend_start] AND [weekend_end];

user_question: Find tech conferences in Berlin during August 2025.

user_question: What theater shows are playing in New York?
expected_sql_query: SELECT e.name, v.name, o.start_at_utc FROM events e JOIN categories c ON e.category_id = c.id JOIN event_occurrences o ON e.id = o.event_id JOIN venues v ON o.venue_id = v.id WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(c.name, '$.en') LIKE '%Theater%' AND (JSON_EXTRACT(v.city, '$.en') LIKE '%New York%' OR v.state_id IN (SELECT id FROM states WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(name, '$.en') = 'New York'));

user_question: Find free events happening in Chicago tonight.
expected_sql_query: SELECT e.name, o.start_at_utc FROM events e JOIN event_occurrences o ON e.id = o.event_id JOIN venues v ON o.venue_id = v.id JOIN event_occurrence_ticket_definition eotd ON o.id = eotd.event_occurrence_id JOIN ticket_definitions td ON eotd.ticket_definition_id = td.id WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(v.city, '$.en') LIKE '%Chicago%' AND td.price = 0 AND o.start_at_utc BETWEEN [tonight_start] AND [tonight_end] GROUP BY e.id;

user_question: How much are tickets for the 'Future of AI' event?

user_question: What are the cheapest concerts I can go to next week?
expected_sql_query: SELECT e.name, MIN(td.price) as min_price FROM events e JOIN categories c ON e.category_id = c.id JOIN event_occurrences o ON e.id = o.event_id JOIN event_occurrence_ticket_definition eotd ON o.id = eotd.event_occurrence_id JOIN ticket_definitions td ON eotd.ticket_definition_id = td.id WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(c.name, '$.en') LIKE '%Concerts%' AND o.start_at_utc BETWEEN [next_week_start] AND [next_week_end] GROUP BY e.id ORDER BY min_price ASC;

user_question: Are VIP tickets still available for the 'Synthwave Summer Fest'?
expected_sql_query: SELECT e.name, td.name, td.status, eotd.availability_status FROM events e JOIN event_occurrences o ON e.id = o.event_id JOIN event_occurrence_ticket_definition eotd ON o.id = eotd.event_occurrence_id JOIN ticket_definitions td ON eotd.ticket_definition_id = td.id WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(e.name, '$.en') LIKE '%Synthwave Summer Fest%' AND JSON_EXTRACT(td.name, '$.en') LIKE '%VIP%' AND td.status = 'available' AND eotd.availability_status = 'available';

user_question: Find events in Taiwan at venues with a seating capacity over 1,000.
